Q: What is Qt creator?
An IDE for C++ and other programming languages.

Q: How does it works?
qtcreator
File > New file or project > Other project > Empty Qt project       # Create a project (.pro) file
cat hello_world.pro <<EOT
TEMPLATE = app
TARGET = hello_world
QT = core gui
EOT
File > New file or project > C++ > C++ source file                  # Create a hello_world.cpp file with correct entries in .pro file
this operation add in project file
HEADERS += \
           hello_world.h
SOURCES += \
           hello_world.cpp
In hello_wold.cpp add main
cat hello_world.cpp <<EOT
#include <QApplication>
#include <QPushButton>
 
int main(int argc, char **argv)
{
    QApplication app (argc, argv);
 
    QPushButton button ("Hello world !");
    button.show();
 
    return app.exec();
} 
EOT



